name: Johnson Brown
description:
I consider myself a loving man, I love to be surrounded by people with a good sense of humor. I am humble, kind, respectful and charismatic. I am family-oriented and well-mannered. I think life must be enjoyed to the fullest!
I want to find a kind, honest, sincere woman to be my princess
I want to meet a woman who is reliable, kind and has a good sense of humor. I dream to create harmonious, comfort and a strong family based on love and caring about each other! I want us to love, care, laugh and always be sure of each other. My woman should not be perfect. She should just be right for me.
